results

# Local caches, tooling state and campaign artefacts: never inputs to an image
# build. The benchmark tree ships in the image, so the context is no longer just
# the crate — keep the junk beside it out.
# The `**/` matters: a bare pattern is matched against the whole path, so
# `.ruff_cache` alone would only exclude one at the repo root — not the ones
# ruff leaves next to the Python kernels.
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.pytest_cache
**/__pycache__
**/.claude
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/*.ndjson
**/*.csv
